  <brief_title>The Designer D-dimer Deep Vein Thrombosis Diagnosis (4D) Study</brief_title>
  <acronym>4D</acronym>
  <official_title>D-dimer Testing, Tailored to Clinical Pretest Probability, to Minimize Initial and Follow-up Ultrasound Imaging in Suspected Deep Vein Thrombosis: A Management Study</official_title>
